com.mousebird.maply

Interface RemoteTileSource.TileSourceDelegate

  • Enclosing class:
    RemoteTileSource

    public static interface RemoteTileSource.TileSourceDelegate
    The tile source delegate will be called back when a tile loads or fails to load.

    You use these for tracking what the remote tile source is up to. They're not required, but they are handy for capturing failures.
